## Bench Constraints (apply everywhere)

- **Never edit** `apps/{frappe,erpnext,crm,hrms,lending,lms,education,helpdesk,gameplan,drive,press}/` — upstream, read-only. Custom work lives in `apps/{novizna_crm,novizna_core,novizna_pos,invoice_ninja_integration,noviznaerp_payroll,cargo_management,changemakers,erpnext_location}/`.
