- **Bench restart** requires typing the **site name** (`{{ bench.primary_site }}`), not "yes".
- **Type annotations + PEP 257 docstrings** on every Python function.
- **No `frappe.db.commit()` inside `doc_events`** handlers. **No f-string interpolation in `frappe.db.sql`** — use `values=`. **Justify every `ignore_permissions=True`** with a one-line comment.

